node.text: What’s best way to end Saturday with a bowl of happiness ❤️. Homemade Durian Mango Pomelo Sago dessert by Lam Sisters. We added durian gelato from @alferogelato and perfect 👌. Alfredo Gelato is offering 15% off till 1 June when you shop at their e-shop (min. order of above S$70). Simply key in “COUPON15” when you check out. #hzfooddiary #homemadedessert
